Name: Brick BiuBiu
About the game: A simple and casual shooting elimination game. Eliminate the bricks and get a higher score! The player moves the actor to move left and right, send bullets, a line of bricks are filled, you can get scores. As the score increases, the speed of generating new bricks also increases. In hard mode, brick generation also moves left and right. When the brick hits the actor, game is over.
